<p id="message_begin">Welcome to Unhinged. At any time you may press the button on the bottom left for the menu, or type "help" for a list of commands that you may use.</p>

<p id="message_help">Help: (replace the italicized words to utilize the commands)<br />
take <i>object</i>: takes the specified object and puts it in your inventory<br />
eat <i>food</i>: eats indicated food item<br />
battle <i>enemy</i> with <i>object</i>: fights indicated enemy with specified object<br />
inventory: lists everything you are currently carrying<br />
unlock <i>door</i> with <i>object</i>: unlocks door with the object you specify<br />
go <i>direction</i>: attempts to travel in direction (north, east, south, west)<br />
search <i>object</i>: searches the indicated object for items</p>

