<!--Story Begins-->
<p id="area_start">You find yourself inside of a dark and chilly room. You have no idea how you got here. Directly in front of you is an exit to the room. You consider searching around the room to see if theres anything useful. You notice a shield lying there.</p>

<p id="area_castle">You have entered the castle. To the west and to the east are long dark hallways. To the south is the  room from where you came. The only source of light is a torch hanging on the wall. Beneath the torch lies a mysterious note. Perhaps it was left by your captors.</p>

<p id="area_village">You have entered a village that seems to be a place of great anguish. Strange and grotesque looking inhabitants roam the streets. There's a slingshot lying in the grass. After a quick observation, you notice that the village appears fairly large, and a hut sits in the corner. To the south there is a wasteland of sand. To the west is the castle that you came from.</p>
